    TorreyPinesSouth.gpx
    Full 18-hole simulation at Torrey Pines South Course, La Jolla, CA.

    Verification table (tee to green distance):
    Hole 1:  Tee (32.9014, -117.2533) → Green (32.8998, -117.2520) ≈ 452 yards ± 10
    Hole 10: Tee (32.8974, -117.2495) → Green (32.8964, -117.2485) ≈ 312 yards ± 10
    Hole 18: Tee (32.8964, -117.2528) → Green (32.8951, -117.2501) ≈ 570 yards ± 10

    Each hole:
      1. Tee box position
      2. Mid-fairway approach (~200 yards out)
      3. Short game position (~100 yards out)
      4. Green approach (~40 yards out)
      5. Green center (stationary mode trigger — 6x repeats at 10s intervals)

    GPS blackout simulation: 60-second gap in segment 18 (test GPSLoss behavior)
  -->

